E-Commerce API
🚀 Features
👨‍💻 Admin

✅ Create categories & subcategories

✅ Add products with details (price, description, images)

✅ Add product variants (sizes, colors, etc.)

✅ Manage inventory (stock updates when orders are placed)

🛍️ Customer

🔎 Browse categories

🔎 Search & filter products

🛒 Add items to cart, update or remove them

📦 Place orders from cart

📉 System auto-deducts stock from inventory

📌 API Endpoints
🩺 Health & Auth
Method	Endpoint	Description
GET	/health_check/	API health check
POST	/user/signup/	User signup (customer)
POST	/admin/signup/	Admin signup
POST	/login/	Login (admin/customer)


👨‍💻 Admin Routes
Method	Endpoint	Description
POST	/admin/category/	Create category/subcategory
POST	/admin/products/	Add new product
POST	/admin/variant/	Add product variant


🛍️ Customer Routes
Method	Endpoint	Description
GET	/categories/	Browse categories
GET	/products/list/	List products (supports search & filter)
POST	/cart/	Add product variant to cart
PUT	/cart/<item_id>/	Update quantity in cart
DELETE	/cart/<item_id>/	Remove item from cart
POST	/orders/	Place an order from cart


🔄 Example Requests
POST - /login/
{
  "email": "marykom2@gmail.com",
  "password": "Mary1234#"
}

🛒 Add Product to Cart (Customer)

POST /cart/

{
  "variant_id": "variant-uuid",
  "quantity": 2
}

